plot: Three amateur adventurers accept a quest from the town's lord. Their challenge: survive a perilous world teeming with thieves, orcs, goblins, wizards, and witches, despite their inexperience.

Three adventurers aspire to a quest given by the lord in a town where they stay. Only one problem remains: to survive, albeit disgracefully, in a dangerous world filled with thieves, orcs, goblins, wizards and witches, even though they are incredibly amateurs.
